#: ../../source/drawing_animation_levels.rst:309
msgid ""
"When the Viewer work area is rotated, guides are rotated as well, but "
"rulers and guide markers will preserve their position and orientation. "
"However the position of a guide will still be controlled by markers, even"
" if they visually don’t match anymore."
